===Verb===
{{en-verb|kibitzes|kibitzing|kibitzed|kibitzed}}
# {{intransitive}} To give [[advice]] when it is not wanted, especially to someone playing a [[game]].
#:'' Quit '''kibitzing'''!  You're giving away my hand! ''
# {{intransitive}} To [[chat]]; to [[gossip]]; to make [[small talk]]
#:'' Louise and I used to head down to the coffee shop and just sit for hours and '''kibitz'''. ''

